### OTA 예약 요청 수신 (야놀자)
### 순서: 호텔 등록 → 객실 타입 등록 → 이 요청 실행
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otaChannel": "YANOLJA",
  "otaReservationId": "YANOLJA-RES-001",
  "roomTypeId": 1,
  "guestName": "홍길동",
  "guestPhone": "010-1234-5678",
  "checkInDate": "2026-05-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-05-03",
  "totalPrice": 200000
}

###

### OTA 예약 요청 수신 (여기어때)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otaChannel": "YEOGI",
  "otaReservationId": "YEOGI-RES-001",
  "roomTypeId": 1,
  "guestName": "김철수",
  "guestPhone": "010-9876-5432",
  "checkInDate": "2026-05-01",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-05-02",
  "totalPrice": 100000
}

###

### OTA 예약 요청 수신 (요기서)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/ota/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "otaChannel": "YOGISEO",
  "otaReservationId": "YOGISEO-RES-001",
  "roomTypeId": 1,
